kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次坐老細車，見到冷氣位有隻小強屍攝住係啲橫條bar入面。可能就係因為冇閂好窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw你好有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c1919732f237fa4bc62113eab4103d76fa059e","tid":493772,"uid":37713,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時冬天天氣凍啲貓會懶訓少少<br />\n最好都係拍兩拍啦"},{"pid":"6e5afbbf837f8de614cb8a509d5cccbef8c45c51","tid":493772,"uid":2655,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年冬天有日我開左少少窗諗住等貓仔可以捐入去<br />\n點知第朝拎車果陣真係有隻貓係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此就開少少窗順便抖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔驚比人偷野？"},{"pid":"7f04f60c26539fa6d801ee4f1491f70cb6c31764","tid":493772,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時冬天天氣凍啲貓會懶訓少少<br />\n最好都係拍兩拍啦</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad2319010a9e5c641f386a82abf508ae48e825c","tid":493772,"uid":102197,"like":29,"dislike":206,"score":-177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"好想車撚死d貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔見你講其他動物？"},{"pid":"1069d0a7d3f7216a46dd44abae9d66f30a7a46f4","tid":493772,"uid":28163,"like":573,"dislike":50,"score":523,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"上次有隻牛訓係車底<br />\n我無為意<br />\n一開車 變左 免治牛肉<br />\n夜晚飯錢都慳埋"},{"pid":"c9fec1b79ff927752c7c9e9dbccfeb7ec1940496","tid":493772,"uid":84212,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6da63af20963daebfaf36316c004250f947986f